@defis_eu

Vaccines are safe and effective for expectant mothers.

@EMA has reviewed several studies involving around 65,000 pregnancies and found out that vaccines do not cause pregnancy complications. 

#SafeVaccines https://t.co/erw9TBnwYV

@EMA_News Are vaccines safe for pregnant women?  

Yes! Vaccines reduce the risk of hospitalisation or death during pregnancy.  

If you contract #COVID19 during pregnancy, you are at higher risk of serious illness or delivering a baby prematurely. https://t.co/nRivjWq8Tx
